{"tid":181302,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好憎松井珠理奈 （3）","createTime":"2017-03-31T14:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T15:41:40.000Z","uid":98322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e30cee612c5c4269231d8dae1bb87527054a433","tid":181302,"uid":98322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T14:02:38.000Z","msg":"救世珠而家一定嬲撚到仆街，本身坐定粒六睇你班長老唔選。今年又冇左第1，紅白又得11位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/31/215854_862d992e0460fa39917b8324f1fd3e0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F31%2F215854_862d992e0460fa39917b8324f1fd3e0d.jpg&h=3e95600d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁以後點樣救ske呀？人地專登解除akb兼任架，要一本ske<br />\n<br />\n而家指原 麻友已遞表<br />\n同佢追得越黎越貼近既櫻花都遞埋<br />\n<br />\n金髮真係好靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/26/214516_d0dc79ee507fc3cb9cdbd39c53a1b212.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F26%2F214516_d0dc79ee507fc3cb9cdbd39c53a1b212.jpg&h=330dcb70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>萬年次世代 package</strong><br />\n樣，唔突出<br />\n身材，唔突出<br />\n談吐，得罪人多<br />\n跳舞，勁誇張<br />\n唱歌，唔敢生唱<br />\n演技，0<br />\n<br />\n上個post有人總結左佢2017年既柒事<br />\n生日倒數，娘娘con提高娘娘條裙事件，311同女王去聯誼，48single W cetre，染金毛，成人式言論，班飯搞搞陣事件，2專宣傳事件<br />\n<br />\n<strong>松井珠理奈歷年豐功偉績</strong><br />\n猜拳女王<br />\nrequest hour史上初連霸偉業達成 15-16年<br />\nSKE centre 18回<br />\n出道以來連續AKB選拔<br />\n大top<br />\n有專車接送,洗費揮霍<br />\n1流藝能事務所所屬<br />\n單獨CM<br />\n兼任AKB名義TV出演多數（含特番）<br />\n2套電視劇（其中一套為女主角）<br />\n<br />\n結果：<br />\n生寫真買取價格：300yen以下<br />\n寫真集銷量：3萬<br />\ntwitter followers：14萬<br />\n紅白總選：11位<br />\n浴衣祭舞台events：未完賣[/quote]"},{"pid":"e6d166dc33d7bd20c02f579378f06d91e52c6861","tid":181302,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T14:09:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34497c5eca1d81027e41d111ae58d0894db7be5a","tid":181302,"uid":39630,"like":0